Package: Synth.Infer
Type: Package
Title: Statistical Inference for Average Treatment Effects Estimated by Synthetic Control
    Methods
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0)
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Kathleen", "Li", role = c("cre", "aut"), email = "kathleen.li@mccombs.utexas.edu"),
    person("Chi", "Zhang", role = "aut", email = "mayson.zhang@utexas.edu"))
Description: Implements formal inference method that can be used to obtain confidence intervals and conduct inference whereas the standard bootstrap cannot. For more information about this subsampling method, please refer to the paper Statistical Inference for Average Treatment Effects Estimated by Synthetic Control Methods (Li, 2019).
Imports: 
    pracma,
    ggplot2
